---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
import Button from "../components/UI/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Soy nuevo aquí - Alianza Vida Abundante"
  description="Todo lo que necesitas saber sobre asistir a nuestros eventos por primera vez. Encuentra horarios, qué esperar y cómo conectarte."
  transition:name="nav-trans"
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="Soy nuevo aquí" 
    subtitle="¡Bienvenido! Nos alegra que estés considerando acompañarnos."
    backgroundImage="/uploads/logo.webp"
  />
  
  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Primero</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Elije la actividad que más te interese y haz clic en el botón para obtener más información.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="card text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#3e45b5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Formación Pastoral</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Formación Pastoral es una iniciativa continua que reúne periódicamente a los miembros y amigos de AVA, con el propósito de fortalecer a los edificadores mediante enseñanza bíblica, ministración espiritual y espacios de comunidad ministerial.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jpBKY1kZDVA&list=PLxnZIeiBlkVj3jY2k6p1BnhXk1tJkt80v" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700" target="_blank">
            Ver última Formación Pastoral →
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-secondary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#f76c33">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
              d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v12a1 1 0 01-1 1h-7v3h3m-6 0h3m-3 0H9m6-8h2a1 1 0 000-2h-2v2zM5 13h6v-2H5v2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Masterclass</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Masterclass es un espacio de desarrollo dirigido a líderes que edifican el Reino de Dios dentro y fuera de la iglesia. A través de enseñanzas profundas y aplicadas, el pastor Juan Spyker expone principios bíblicos, ayudando a los líderes a crecer más.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KQ6egltT5Jc&list=PLxnZIeiBlkVjq_92c_W4sUo58nPgd8mFg" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700" target="_blank">
            Ver última Masterclass →
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #e8d5af;">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-accent-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#7a6254">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Conferencia Fiel</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Conferencia FIEL es un encuentro anual para pastores y líderes comprometidos con servir a la iglesia con integridad y fidelidad. Cada año, Dios renueva el corazón del ministro y afirma su llamado en un ambiente centrado en la Palabra y la presencia de Dios.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z1zE-1loXAU&list=PLxnZIeiBlkVjBWeIAo30mnRvhKqgB5xHy" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700" target="_blank">
            Ver última Conferencia Fiel →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What to Wear -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529626455594-4ff0802cfb7e?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" 
            alt="Casual church attire" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">What to Wear</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">
            We want you to feel comfortable when you visit. You'll find people dressed in everything from casual (jeans and t-shirts) to business casual (slacks and button-ups or dresses).
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">
            Our priority is that you join us, not what you wear. Come as you are, and know you'll be welcomed warmly!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Service Times -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Service Times</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Join us for worship at any of our weekly services
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Sunday Morning</h3>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">8:00 AM</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Traditional Service</p>
            <p class="italic text-gray-500 mt-2">In-person & Livestream</p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">10:30 AM</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Contemporary Service with Children's Ministry</p>
            <p class="italic text-gray-500 mt-2">In-person only</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Wednesday Evening</h3>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">7:00 PM</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Mid-week Prayer & Bible Study</p>
            <p class="italic text-gray-500 mt-2">In-person & Livestream</p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">7:00 PM</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Youth Group (Grades 6-12)</p>
            <p class="italic text-gray-500 mt-2">In-person only</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- For Kids -->
  <section id="kids" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">For Families with Children</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">
            We love children and believe they are an important part of our church family. Here's what we offer for kids:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Nursery (0-2 years):</strong> Safe, loving care for our littlest ones during all services.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Preschool (3-5 years):</strong> Age-appropriate activities, Bible stories, and fun during the 10:30 AM service.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Elementary (K-5th grade):</strong> Interactive lessons, games, and worship during the 10:30 AM service.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">
            All our children's ministry volunteers undergo background checks and are trained to provide a safe, nurturing environment.
          </p>
          
          <Button href="/ministries/childrens-ministry">
            Learn More About Children's Ministry
          </Button>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503454537195-1dcabb73ffb9?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" 
            alt="Children at our church" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Location & Directions -->
  <section id="location" class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Location & Directions</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We're easy to find and have plenty of parking
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden h-96">
            <!-- Placeholder for Google Maps iframe -->
            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-300">
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center p-4">
                Google Maps embed would go here<br>
                <span class="text-sm">(For privacy reasons, not included in the template)</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm h-full">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Church Address</h3>
            <address class="not-italic mb-6 text-gray-700">
              <p class="text-lg">123 Main Street</p>
              <p class="text-lg">Anytown, ST 12345</p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">
                  (555) 123-4567
                </a>
              </p>
            </address>
            
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Parking Information</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              We have a large parking lot on the north side of the building with designated visitor parking near the main entrance. Handicap parking is available near both the north and south entrances.
            </p>
            
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Public Transportation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Bus lines 10 and 14 stop directly in front of our building. The nearest subway station is Central Station, a 10-minute walk from our church.
            </p>
            
            <Button href="https://maps.google.com/?q=123+Main+Street,+Anytown,+ST+12345" target="_blank" variant="primary">
              Get Directions
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section id="faq" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Answers to common questions from first-time visitors
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Where do I go when I arrive?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            When you arrive, look for our welcome team members wearing blue name tags. They'll greet you, help you check in your children if needed, and direct you to the sanctuary or any other areas you'd like to visit.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Will I be asked to stand up or introduce myself?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            No, we won't single you out or ask you to stand up. We want you to feel comfortable, not put on the spot. We do have a welcome card in the service bulletin if you'd like to share your information with us.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Is there a coffee hour or fellowship time?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            Yes! We have coffee, tea, and light refreshments available before and after each service in our fellowship hall. It's a great opportunity to meet people and ask any questions you might have.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Do you have facilities for nursing mothers?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            Yes, we have a comfortable, private nursing mothers' room adjacent to the nursery. It's equipped with changing facilities, comfortable seating, and a live audio feed of the service.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">How do I get connected beyond Sunday services?</h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            The best way to get connected is through our small groups and ministry teams. Visit our welcome center after the service, and we'll help you find the right fit. You can also attend our "New to Church Name" class, offered monthly.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
  
  <!-- Plan Your Visit CTA -->
  <section id="volunteer" class="py-20 bg-cover bg-center text-white"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url(/uploads/visit-us.webp"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Ready to Visit?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">
          We look forward to meeting you this Sunday. If you have any questions before your visit, please don't hesitate to contact us.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" size="lg">
            Contact Us
          </Button>
          
          <Button href="https://maps.google.com/?q=123+Main+Street,+Anytown,+ST+12345" target="_blank" variant="outline" size="lg" class="bg-white/10 text-white border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 backdrop-blur-sm">
            Get Directions
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>